OL,4,Cas Government vows to repeal Legacy Act
OL,6,FWhile the entire Act cannot be
OL,7,Frepealed without something to replace
OL,8,Fit, the Government is expected to
OL,9,Frepeal the controversial policy of
OL,10,Foffering conditional immunity for
OL,11,FTroubles crimes among first steps.
OL,13,FThe Act, aimed at addressing the
OL,14,Flegacy of Northern Ireland's past, has
OL,15,Fbeen almost universally opposed by
OL,16,Fparties and victims' groups.
