OL,4,Cas Government vows to repeal Legacy Act
OL,6,FIt offers a limited form of immunity
OL,7,Ffor perpetrators of Troubles crimes in
OL,8,Fexchange for full co-operation with
OL,9,Fthe truth recovery body, the
OL,10,FIndependent Commission for
OL,11,FReconciliation and Information
OL,12,FRecovery (Icrir), and halted civil
OL,13,Fcases and inquests which were not at
OL,14,Ffindings stage earlier this year.
OL,16,FMartina Dillon, whose husband Seamus
OL,17,Fwas shot and killed in 1997, was among
OL,18,Fthose who saw a fresh inquest into a
OL,19,Floved one's death stopped due to the
OL,20,FAct.
