OL,6,FShe said she was relieved to hear the
OL,7,Fcommitment to repeal, adding ministers
OL,8,Fneed to "follow through quickly".
OL,10,FShe added: "I've fought for 27 years
OL,11,Fto get truth and justice for my
OL,12,Fhusband. I had an inquest under way,
OL,13,Fto then have that cruelly removed by
OL,14,Fthe Troubles Act has been devastating.
OL,16,F"All victims deserve answers and
OL,17,Fvictim-centred processes. Truth and
OL,18,Fjustice are not much to ask, we
OL,19,Fshouldn't have to fight for decades to
OL,20,Fget it."
