OL,6,FMichael O'Hare's 12-year-old sister
OL,7,FMajella was shot and killed by a
OL,8,FBritish soldier on her way to church
OL,9,Fwith a group of friends in 1976. He
OL,10,Fsaid his family believed the door for
OL,11,Fjustice had been closed.
OL,13,F"This is an important day for families
OL,14,Flike ours, who thought we'd seen the
OL,15,Fdoor closed forever on these cases,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,18,F"Majella was just an innocent little
OL,19,Fgirl who didn't deserve to be gunned
OL,20,Fdown when walking along the road with
OL,21,Fher friends.
