OL,3,CTroubles bereaved hail 'important day'
OL,4,Cas Government vows to repeal Legacy Act
OL,6,FThe new Labour Government is to stick
OL,7,Fto its General Election manifesto
OL,8,Fcommitment to address legacy, aiming
OL,9,Fto find a way forward supported by
OL,10,Fvictims and survivors, and which will
OL,11,Fcomply with human rights organisations.
OL,13,FThis is to include repealing the
OL,14,Fconditional immunity scheme and
OL,15,Freversing the policy prohibiting
OL,16,Fvictims and families from bringing
OL,17,Fcivil claims, and set out steps to
OL,18,Fallow the Troubles-era inquests that
OL,19,Fwere prematurely halted to resume.
